Anubis.en:
New Stuff

Yeah, well, have you seen the new Mustang? You could hump that hood. Michael, I'm your older brother.

I'll never be proud of you. And the soup of the day is bread. Are all the guys in here… you know? George Sr: No not all of them. Barry: Yeah. It's never the ones you hope. Excuse me, do these effectively hide my thunder? Well, if you want to play Eve, you got to get in line behind what, above five homos. Whenever she'd change clothes, she'd make me wait on the balcony until zip-up, and yet anything goes at bath time.

He's going to be all right.
